1. Resistance exercise (RT) can enhance muscle protein synthesis (MPS).
2. A study was conducted to examine the effect of RT on MPS after 2 weeks of sleep restriction (SR).
3. The duration of the sleep restriction in the study was 2 weeks.

messages.content:
Statement: Knowing that resistance exercise (RT) can enhance MPS, we examined whether RT could enhance MPS following 2 weeks of SR.

List all the facts we explicitly know from the statement. Make each fact as atomic as possible.
